"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35533,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/04\/disobedient-gain-upper-hand\/","url_meta":{"origin":10974,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sins: Entire nation punished if disobedient gain upper hand","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 4, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen the disobedient gain ascendancy in my nation, Allah Almighty will send down His punishment upon all of them.\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, will there be righteous among them on that day?\u201d The Prophet\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41281,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/29\/eisa-ummah\/","url_meta":{"origin":10974,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ummah: Allah tells Jesus about Muhammad\u2019s nation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 29, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty said: O Jesus, I will raise a nation after you who will praise Me and be grateful to Me when I bestow what they love, and they will expect reward and be patient when\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33804,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/11\/21\/the-prophet-intercedes-ummah\/","url_meta":{"origin":10974,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Shafa&#8217;a: The Prophet intercedes for sinners of the Ummah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 21, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cMy intercession is for the people of major sins among my nation.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2435 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0634\u064e\u0641\u064e\u0627\u0639\u064e\u062a\u0650\u064a \u0644\u0650\u0623\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0643\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0631\u0650 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0645\u0651\u064e\u062a\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8133,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/14\/khayr-ummah-lil-nas-companions\/","url_meta":{"origin":10974,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: Best nation raised up for people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa'id ibn Jubary reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \"Alla